(351, 352, '0x0100000B00000430', 'ICE / EGGHEAD', 'Side-dialogue. Has the Physical Instrument check that makes Andre\'s Composure dance check easier and initiates the TO:DO - Make Van Eyck\'s jam more hard core', '396', '16'),
(352, 353, '0x0100000B00000437', 'ICE / ANDRE', 'Talking to the speedfreaks\' leader', '396', '14'),
(353, 354, '0x0100000B00002929', 'BACKYARD / MOTHER OF ALL WALLS', 'Stop everything and direct all attention to that wall -- it\'s sublime!', '396', '355'),
(354, 355, '0x0100000B0000400A', 'WHIRLING F2 ORB / ashtray', 'Looks like she left a nice long stub in the ashtray. It\'s still smoking.', '0', '0'),
(355, 356, '0x0100000B00004017', 'WHIRLING F2 ORB / dialogue cigarette stub', 'ashtray dialogue / TASK find smokes', '0', '0'),
(356, 357, '0x0100000B000040EA', 'WHIRLING F1 ORB / dialogue home', 'where is home, what is home afterthought', '0', '0'),
(357, 358, '0x0100000F00006E2C', 'WHIRLING F2 ORB / Communist Quest Initiation', 'Rhetoric tells you it\'s time to bone up on dialectical materialism and get organized.', '0', '0'),
(358, 359, '0x0100000F0000707C', 'Get yourself organised', 'You can\'t build communism alone. It\'s time to join your revolutionary brethren, develop your political consciousness, and put Mazovian theory into practice. But where have all the communists gone?', '0', '0'),
(359, 360, '0x0100000F000070BA', 'GATES ORB / communistquest', 'Rhetoric smells a communist around here. Part of the Communist Dream Quest', '0', '0'),
(360, 361, '0x0100000F000072B8', 'APT / COMMUNIST MEETING DOOR', 'Door leading to the Storage Room where the Secret Communist Meeting takes place. (PART OF THE COMMUNIST DREAM QUEST)', '0', '0'),
(361, 362, '0x0100000F00007585', 'APT / STUDENT COMMUNIST', 'The Student Communist and his underground reading group (PART OF THE COMMUNIST DREAM QUEST)', '396', '126'),
(362, 363, '0x0100000F00007989', 'PIER ORB / communistquest', 'Rhetoric smells a communist around here. Part of the Communist Dream Quest', '0', '0'),
(363, 364, '0x0100000F00008436', 'INVENTORY / LA FUMEE', 'Vol. 1 No. 2 of *La Fumée*, Martinaise\'s leading quarterly journal of radical Mazovian thought (PART OF THE COMMUNIST DREAM QUEST)', '0', '0'),
(364, 365, '0x0100000F0000843D', 'INVENTORY / INFRA-MATERIALISM GUIDE', 'An Introduction to the Theories of Ignus Nilsen (PART OF THE COMMUNIST DREAM QUEST)', '0', '0'),
(365, 366, '0x0100000F0000BC86', 'WHIRLING F2 ORB / Moralist Quest Initiation', 'Empathy tells you it\'s time to take responsibility... by convening a committee to spread responsibility around.', '0', '0'),
(366, 367, '0x0100000F0000BEC9', 'Take on *la responsabilité*', 'Things down here are a *mess*. Someone really ought to do something about it. First, though, you and some other moralists should probably form a committee to decide whose job it is.', '0', '0'),
(367, 368, '0x0100000F0000BF28', 'JAM / COALITION WARSHIP ARCHER -- NOID VERSION', 'CUTSCENE where you attempt to contact Coalition Warship Archer with NOID. PART OF THE MORALIST DREAM QUEST', '396', '15'),
(368, 369, '0x0100000F0000E7AE', 'OFFICE / SECRETARYS RADIO', 'You can remove the transceiver from this radio as part of the MORALIST DREAM QUEST', '0', '0'),
(369, 370, '0x0100000F0000EA1F', 'COAST ORB / Empathy Afterthought', 'There\'s no way you\'ll reach the Coalition with this piece of junk...', '0', '0'),
(370, 371, '0x0100000F0000EA29', 'WESTCOAST / SUNDAY FRIEND', 'PART OF THE MORALIST DREAM QUEST. You come across the Sunday friend enjoying the historical scenery. You also have the chance to apologise if you accused him earlier.', '0', '0'),
(371, 372, '0x0100000F00011584', 'WHIRLING F2 ORB / Ultraliberal Quest Initiation', 'Savoir Faire tells you it\'s time to stop playing the market and make some real cash so you can fulfil your heart\'s desire.', '0', '0'),
(372, 373, '0x0100000F00011829', 'Become a man of plenty', 'No more messing around. It\'s time to get rich for real! Just play the market right and you\'ll be a millionaire by the end of the week. Then you can get what your heart desires. Whatever it is...', '0', '0'),
(373, 374, '0x0100000F0001183F', 'PIER ORB / ultraliberal quest pre-cindy', 'Savoir Faire spots Cindy and gives you a pep talk before you try to negotiate for her art.', '0', '0'),
(374, 375, '0x0100000F0001200E', 'CONTAINERYARD ORB / ultraliberal dream quest', 'Savoir Faire hears wealth humming in the container -- whether it\'s raised or lowered. Also gives you instant access to MRLBG.', '0', '0'),
(375, 376, '0x0100000F0001476A', 'INVENTORY / STOCK CERTIFICATE', 'Read the Stock Certificate traded with MRLBG', '0', '0'),
(376, 377, '0x0100000F000149FB', 'JAM / MONUMENT REFLECTION', 'After the Tribunal, Harry reflects on the re-conceptualization of the horseback monument by Idiot Doom Spiral. (ULTRALIBERAL DREAM QUEST)', '0', '0'),
(377, 378, '0x01000014000006CB', 'GATES / SCAB LEADER', 'Scab Leader, a large mercenary in disguise. Shouts a lot about LETTING US WORK, doesn\'t actually provide much information for now, except being suspicious and shouting.', '396', '36'),
(378, 379, '0x010000140000087B', 'GATES / MANANA', 'A jolly, easy-going man at the very bottom entrance to the gates. He gives information about the scabs, the strike, the union boss, Measurehead and being a boiadeiro.', '396', '39'),
(379, 380, '0x010000140000146C', 'ICE / NOID', 'Noid dialogue -- happens mostly inside church.', '396', '15'),
(380, 381, '0x0100001400002523', 'GATES / MEASUREHEAD', 'An übermensch monolith guarding the button to the harbour office door. Into \"science\"-anthropometry based racial theory.', '396', '38'),
(381, 382, '0x0100001600001D03', 'WHIRLING / SLEEPING DOCKWORKER', 'Downstairs at the Whirling In Rags there\'s a sleeping dockworker. Interfacing people can steal his wallet and work pass, Phys inst can wake him up by yelling and then get some info on the Union and the strike.', '396', '9'),
(382, 383, '0x0100001600002B2A', 'PLAZA / RENE', 'René is in the shade, the forlorn option who\'s losing at the game.', '396', '57'),
(383, 384, '0x0100001600002BA6', 'PLAZA ORB / gaston cheating', 'Cheating!', '396', '58'),
(384, 385, '0x0100001600002BBE', 'PLAZA / RENE barks', 'Playing pétanque.', '57', '0'),
(385, 386, '0x0100001600002BC4', 'PLAZA / GASTON barks', 'Playing pétanque and cheating.', '58', '0'),
(386, 387, '0x0100001600002F1B', 'PLAZA ORB / crack', 'Some great tectonic force has cracked the pavement, like an eggshell.', '0', '0'),
(387, 388, '0x01000016000089F7', 'Talk to Garte, Lieutenant Love', 'Garte + Sylvie = ?? Something\'s going on here. You need to help a brother out with his love-woes. Go to Garte and give him some solid advice. Tell him how it *is* with women.', '0', '0'),
(388, 389, '0x0100001600008A31', 'Where is the rest of the armour?', 'The hanged man\'s armour seems to be missing. Find out what happened to it. The kid throwing rocks at the corpse seems to be a good place to start. (Ask him about the body first.)', '0', '0'),
(389, 390, '0x0100001600008B65', 'CANAL ORB / waterlock sign afterthought', 'Is this the water lock Lena mentioned?', '0', '0'),
(390, 391, '0x0100001600008D12', 'CHURCH ORB / took cut of lab', 'Aha, the drug lab! Can\'t wait for the profits to start rolling in...', '0', '0'),
(391, 392, '0x01000016000090E3', 'Inspect the traps', 'Check the traps for Morell the cryptozoologist, so he and his friend Gary can get some rest. There are four traps in total. After checking them all, return to Morell with the news.', '0', '0'),
(392, 393, '0x0100001600009AE2', 'COAST ORB / feldwindowsbars', 'Bars cover these long, dusty windows.', '0', '0'),
(393, 394, '0x0100001600009B24', 'COAST ORB / dizzyingheights', 'The gusts of wind, the height feels dizzying.', '0', '0'),
