(399, 400, '0x0100002100000EBD', 'Return to the dead body with Kim', 'There\'s a dead body on the Martinaise boardwalk down the coast. Return to it with the lieutenant and decide what to do with it.', '0', '0'),
(400, 401, '0x01000021000020E9', 'ICE ORB / eternite logic', 'Before you, a drawbridge. It can only be lowered from the other side.', '0', '0'),
(401, 402, '0x01000021000020FB', 'COAST ORB / cormorant reaction', 'To your right, a white-bellied cormorant eyes you suspiciously.', '0', '0'),
(402, 403, '0x010000210000223E', 'APT ORB / dont run', 'Don\'t run, okay? Take it slow when exploring the apartment. Be respectful.', '0', '0'),
(403, 404, '0x0100002100002775', 'What happened to the previous forewoman?', 'There are rumours that the previous forewoman of the Union just disappeared, right before the Claires took over. Her daughter called in on the election eve and said she wasn\'t running any more -- or coming to work. What happened?', '0', '0'),
(404, 405, '0x010000270000070A', 'WHIRLING F2 ORB / dialogue pants', 'These are your sleek pants. Put them on and find THE KEY to get out of your room.', '0', '0'),
(405, 406, '0x0100002700000D45', 'WHIRLING / Kim barks', 'Kim tells you he has a menu for questions after he\'s in the team.', '395', '0'),
(406, 407, '0x0100002700000E84', 'WHIRLING F1 ORB / mess hall door', 'A sign reads: \"Mess hall reserved for Union members. Doors open: 16:00.\"', '0', '0'),
(407, 408, '0x0100002700000E8C', 'WHIRLING F1 ORB / mess hall window', 'Inside you catch a glimpse of Union paraphernalia: a strike poster, some red pennants.', '0', '0'),
