(425, 426, '0x0100002700001094', 'WHIRLING F2 ORB / commodore red', 'This magnum-sized bottle of \"Commodore Red\" is empty.', '0', '0'),
(426, 427, '0x0100002700001190', 'JAM / INSTIGATOR CABIN', 'The Instigator is gone but you can still explore the cabin of her abandoned vehicle. This yields some MAJOR foreshadowing.', '396', '262'),
(427, 428, '0x01000027000011A3', 'BOOKSTORE / PLAISANCE', 'Inside the book shop. Speaking with the proprietor.', '396', '17'),
(428, 429, '0x010000270000278C', 'BOOKSTORE / CURTAINS', 'The curtains hanging in front of the back room. Curious trinkets attached. Very suspect. Can open, but Plaisance doesn\'t like that.', '396', '206'),
(429, 430, '0x010000270000289D', 'WHIRLING F2 / KLAASJE DOOR', 'When the dialogue with Klaasje is over you can go and click and her door.', '0', '0'),
(430, 431, '0x010000290000182D', 'Find the Insulindian Phasmid', 'You\'ve volunteered to restock the empty trap for the cryptozoologists. They even gave you fresh box of locusts. This could, after some messing around, *probably* lead to the discovery?', '0', '0'),
(431, 432, '0x0100002B00001373', 'PLAZA / WORKING CLASS DRUNK barks', 'Barks from a working class man with a drinking problem. Triggers an authority orb if you\'ve met the working class woman.', '0', '0'),
(432, 433, '0x0100002B000013BB', 'PLAZA / WORKING CLASS WOMAN', '[Aimée.] A dialogue with a woman who has a job. And a husband. And kids.', '396', '59'),
(433, 434, '0x0100002B00004C37', 'PLAZA ORB / get a drink', 'Start drinking (Electrochem).', '0', '0'),
(434, 435, '0x0100002B00004C3F', 'PLAZA ORB / working class husband', 'AUTHORITY: It\'s a working class woman\'s drunk husband.', '0', '0'),
(435, 436, '0x0100002B00005157', 'PLAZA / COIN-OPERATED VIEWER I', 'A coin-operated viewer on the plaza. It offers a view to the sunken sea-fort.', '203', '0'),
(436, 437, '0x0100002B0000522E', 'PLAZA / COIN-OPERATED VIEWER II', 'A coin-operated viewer on the plaza. It offers a view to the church.', '203', '0'),
(437, 438, '0x0100002B00005235', 'PLAZA ORB / coin-operated viewer III', 'This coin operated viewer has been banged up, inoperable.', '203', '0'),
(438, 439, '0x0100002B000066EC', 'WHIRLING F2 / RADIO barks', 'A radio tuned to an interisolar weather-station.', '0', '0'),
(439, 440, '0x0100002B00006C18', 'Find booze and drink it', 'The hangover feels really bad. You have to take the edge off. Find a bottle of alcohol, put it in your hand (equip it in the HELD slot in your INVENTORY), and the magic will happen by its own!', '0', '0'),
(440, 441, '0x0100002B000081C7', 'Getting the body down', 'Somehow make it so that the bloated corpse isn\'t up there any more. Shoot it down or ask for help. Do something, you\'re a cop.', '0', '0'),
(441, 442, '0x0100002B000082E2', 'Find working class husband', 'The working class woman you met in front of the bookstore admitted that her husband is missing. Chances are the guy is drinking somewhere with his buddies. Find him and bring him home, if possible.', '0', '0'),
(442, 443, '0x0100002B00009100', 'BACKYARD / STONE', 'First follow-up convo with Kim where you discover keys under the stone.', '0', '0'),
(443, 444, '0x0100002B0002388B', 'BACKYARD / KIM barks', 'Kim barks when you step in the courtyard.', '0', '0'),
(444, 445, '0x0100002B0002869B', 'BACKYARD / SMOKER ON THE BALCONY', 'The balcony overlooks the scene of the hanging but he\'s not a witness. He told as much to the investigator before, who you can ascertain was from Whitewater: foreshadowing for the HONOUR COURT\'s arrival later. EDITED VERSION', '7', '0'),
(445, 446, '0x0100002B00029DA1', 'FRITTE / FRITTE CLERK', 'A dialogue with a bored teenage girl who works as a shop clerk.', '396', '395'),
